Indinganiso yamagama ebhizinisi  
Ngokuvumelana nesigatshana , igama lebhizinisi lingase lihlanganise amazwi abhalwe nganoma yiluphi ulimi kungakhathaliseki ukuthi lawo magama avame ukusetshenziswa noma ahloselwe injongo ethile , kanye nanoma yiziphi izinhlamvu zamagama , izinombolo noma izimpawu zokubhala ; 
noma enza noma yini echazwe esigatshaneni ngaphansi kwegama lebhizinisi elibhaliswe komunye umuntu , lowo muntu omunye angase enze isicelo enkantolo sesigunyazo esichazwe esigatshaneni . 
abhalise igama elifanayo lebhizinisi elihunyushelwe kunoma yisiphi isibalo sezilimi ezisemthethweni zaseRiphabhuliki ; 
kokuthintana nabantu abaqhuba ibhizinisi ngaphakathi kwemboni ethintekayo ; 
Umthetho wezimboni kumelwe uvumelane nezinjongo nezinqubomgomo zalo Mthetho . 
Igama , sihloko nencazelo ibhizinisi eliyoqhutshwa ngaphansi kwakho ; 
noma ahoxise yonke noma ingxenye yomthetho owawubhalwe phansi ngaphambilini , ngokutusa kukaKhomishane ngokwemibandela yesigatshana . 
Uma , phakathi nesikhathi igama lebhizinisi elibhaliswe ngalo kumuntu , uMgcini Mibhalo , ngezizathu ezizwakalayo , eholelw ukuthi lowo muntu ubengaliqhubi ibhizinisi ngaphansi kwalelo gama okungenani inkathi engaba yizinyanga eziyisithupha , uMgcini Mibhalo ngesaziso esibhalwe phansi , angase afune umuntu igama lebhizinisi elibhaliswe ngaye abonise isizathu ngendlela ebhaliwe ukuthi kungani ukubhaliswa kwegama kungamelwe kusulwe ; 
noma olawula ukusebenzelana , noma ohlinzeka ngezinye izindlela zokuxazululwa kwezingxabano , phakathi kwabantu abachazwe endimaneni , nabathengi ; 
Ukubhaliswa kwamagama ebhizinisi  
futhi angase asule ukubhalisa ngesaziso ngendlela esibhalwe phansi uma umuntu igama lebhizinisi elibhaliswe ngaye ehluleka ukuphendula isaziso phakathi nesikhathi asinqunyelwe , noma ehluleka ukunikeza ubufakazi obanelisayo bokuthi umuntu uqhuba ibhizinisi ngaphansi kwalelo gama lebhizinisi ; 
noma ukudluliswa kwegama lebhizinisi , njengoba kugcinwe emafayeleni Uma uMgcini Mibhalo ekholelwa ukuthi ngezizathu ezizwakalayo ukuth umuntu uye wenza isicelo sokubhalisa igama lebhizinisi , noma inkumusho yalo noma ukushintsha igama lebhizinisi , elingahambisani nezimfuno zesigaba 81 uMgcini Mibhalo kumelwe azise umenzi wesicelo ngokuvumelana nalokho ; 
Umuntu othonywe yisinqumo soMgcini Mabhuku ngokwemibandela yesigatshana angase afake isicelo eNkantolo Yobulungisa ukuze ihlaziye leso sinqumo . 
noma abakaki abayindilinga abasetshenziswa ngababili ukuze uhlukanise noma iyiphi ingxenye yegama , lodwa noma liyinhlanganisela namanye . 
noma ehluleka ukwenza ngokuvumelana nanoma iyiphi imfuneko yesigaba , uKhomishane angase akhiphe isaziso sokwenza ngokuvumelana kulowo muntu , ngokwemibandela yesigaba 100 ; 
