lingelomuntu , lilawulwa , lixhaswe , lisekelwe noma ligunyazwe noma lijabulela ukuxhaswa ngokwezimali- ngumbuso othile wangaphandle kwezwe , inhloko yombuso , inhloko kahulumeni , uhulumeni noma umnyango ophethe noma ngumnyango othile walowo hulumeni noma umnyango ophethe ; 
