Abeluleko Bezomthetho Bombuso kanye noMnyango Wezohwebo Nezezimboni banomuzwa wokuthi lo Mthetho-Sivivinyo kumelwe ubhekelwe ngokuvumelana nenqubo echazwe yisigaba 76 noma noma uMthetho-Sisekelo njengoba ungena ngaphansi komkhakha osebenzayo ofakwe oHlelweni 4 loMthetho-Sisekelo , okungukuthi ukuvikelwa kwabathengi . 
EMINYE IMINYANGO NEZINDIKIMBA OKUYE KWATHINTWANA NAKO  
Kuhlongozwa ukuba aguqulwe enziwe indikimba eyisishayamthetho . Leli nxusa lizodinga abasebenzi abazoliphelelisa abangu-94 , abangu-31 kubo bazodluliswa besuswa Ophikweni Lokuqondiswa Kwabathengi Nezinkampani . Ngakho-ke kuzodingeka ukuba kugcwaliswe izikhala ezingu-63 esikhathini esizayo . 
Njengoba kuqashelwa injongo ebanzi efezwa yilo Mthetho-Sivivinyo emnothweni wabathengi , kanye nobunzima bokubikezela ngokunembile zonke izinguquko zobuqondiswa ezidingekayo ukuze zivumelaniswe nawo , le mithetho yoguquko inikeza inkululeko yokucabangela izimo ngokuvumela uNgqongqoshe ukuba abambezele ukusebenza kwanoma yimuphi umthetho isikhathi esingaba yizinyanga eziyisithupha ngaphezulu , uma kubonakala ukuthi kudingeka isikhathi esengeziwe ukuze kulungiselelwe ukusebenza komthetho okugculisayo nokwanele . 
Lo Mthetho-Sivivinyo udinga ukuba uKhomishane : Akhuthaze futhi asekele ukwakhiwa kwemakethe nemboni yabathengi engakhethi , engafihli lutho , esimeme , enokuzibophezela , enokwethenjelwa , ephumelelayo nefinyeleleka kalula , ezokhonza ikakhulukazi izidingo zabantu ababeshayelwa amakhala ngaphambilini , abantu nemiphakathi ehola umholo ophansi , nezindawo ezingazodwa eziqhelile nezingenabo abantu abaningi nemiphakathi ; 
Kunikezwa eminye iminyaka eyisithupha ngaphambi imithetho esele iqale ukusebenza futhi imithetho emidala izochithwa . 
