Ukudlulisela izingxabano ezingaxazululwanga ezinkantolo zabathengi zesifundazwe . 
futhi aphenye bese ehlola ukuziphatha okwenqatshelwe okumangalelwe futhi aphoqelele ukuba kwenziwe ngokuvumelana nalo Mthetho . 
