UMthetho-Sivivinyo uhlongoza ukuba kumiswe uKhomishane ozohlinzeka ngokuqondiswa okuphumelelayo kwalo Mthetho ebambisene neNkantolo Yobulungisa Yabathengi Kazwelone . 
