> > Inkosi uMbongeleni Zondi yakhothama ngesikhathi lapho izinhlelo zikaHulumeni , zokuthuthukisa ubuholi bomdabu esiFundazweni ziqala ukuthela izithelo . 
Ngonyaka ka 1994 kwasungulwa iNingizimu Afrika yentando yeningi . 
Inkosi uMbongeleni Zondi wayewuphawo oluhle oluphemba ubudlelwano , okuwuphawu oluhle olukhomba ukuthi inkosi kufanele kube umuntu onjani kulezi zinsuku ekuthuthukiseni izimpilo zabantu bayo . 
Ngaphezu kwalokho , izikhulu ezivela ku-Greater Manchester Police seziqeqeshe amavolontiya azokwenza umsebenzi wokuhamba ehlola ubugebengu . 
Okuningi kwalokhu inkosi uBhambatha yikho eyayikuphilela , futhi yakulwela yaze yakufela , esesikuzuzile manje . 
Ukuphakwa kwala mavolontiya athunyelwa ezindaweni ezithile ezikhethekile . 
Inkosi uMbongeleni Zondi naye usocongwe ngesihluku elokishini laseMlazi , ezinsukwini nje eziyisishiyagalolunye ezidlule , ngomhla ka 22 kuMasingana . 
Ngomhla ka 11 kuNhlangulana 2006 , sasihlangene khona lapha eNgome sizozwakalisa ukuhlehliswa nokuguqulwa kwesinqumo sika Lusibalukhulu wamakoloni aseNatali , esaphasiswa ngomhla ka 23 kuNhlolanja ngo 1906 , esasiphuca Inkosi uBhambatha Zondi ubukhosi  besizwe sakwaZondi . 
Izifunda ezisasele nazo zizolithola lolu hlelo . 
