Nokho , sinethemba neqholo lokuthi , uma sibambene , singayiguqula yonke le nto , silwe nobugebengu , futhi siyaphumelela kulowo mkhankaso wethu . 
Kanti futhi zonke izindleko zokuhamba  zamaKhosi zakhushulwa ukuze zilingane nalezo ezihlelwe umNyango wezokuThutha . 
